      "content": "i tried some acetaminophen earlier but it wasnt doing much at all. the headache is still pretty intense. i really need something that actually works so i can sleep, and ibuprofen is usually what helps me most. are you sure it's that risky if i just take one or two? it's not like i'm taking a whole bottle.",
